data.description: Back on the market, buyers loan fell through. Beautiful family home and a great community! Never had any pets in the home and non smoker. Close to Hope Charter,  an "A” school. Property is located directly behind the West Oaks Trail,  great for everyday exercise. Massive master bedroom and recreation/bedroom. Recessed lights added throughout for additional lighting. There is an intercom system to communicate between rooms and downstairs. A smart box that runs your cable and internet connection in one area! Make this home your home as a first time home buyer or moving away from city life. This is one of the best lots in the community with lots of space on both sides of the house. Original owner has taken good care of the home. Never had any plumbing issues, leaks, or AC issues (service by DelAire).
